{
  "$comment": [
    "出典: Claude Code Development Harness 設計書 Version 1.10",
    "https://github.com/dtakamiya/claudecode-harness-patterns/blob/main/patterns/claude-code-development-harness/docs/design.md",
    "",
    "この雛形は templates/settings.json が配布元であり、利用者の .claude/settings.json へコピーして使う。",
    "",
    "正本: 設計書 §3.5（Deterministic Guardrail）, §3.6（Permission Boundary）, §14.1（Fullモード）",
    "",
    "--- 二層構造であること（重要）---",
    "",
    "permissions.deny と hooks は役割が異なる。どちらか一方では境界にならない。",
    "  permissions.deny … 広いカテゴリの遮断。globで表現できる範囲を担う。",
    "  hooks            … canonical path正規化、create-only、Bashの構造検証。",
    "                     permissionsのglobでは表現できない判定を担う。",
    "設計書 §3.5 は「Hooksだけをサンドボックスやpermissionsの代替にしない」と定める。",
    "",
    "--- permissions.deny を先に書く理由 ---",
    "",
    "hookは実行される前提のガードであり、hookスクリプトが消えた・実行権が落ちた・",
    "シェルが無い等で起動しなければ何も守らない。秘密情報や制御面のパスは、",
    "hookに依存しない permissions.deny 側で先に遮断する。"
  ],

  "permissions": {
    "deny": [
      "Read(./.env)",
      "Read(./.env.*)",
      "Read(./secrets/**)",
      "Read(./docs/archive/**)",

      "Write(./.env)",
      "Write(./.env.*)",
      "Write(./secrets/**)",

      "Write(./.claude/**)",
      "Edit(./.claude/**)",

      "Write(./docs/status/progress.yaml)",
      "Edit(./docs/status/progress.yaml)",

      "Write(./docs/status/gate-runs/**)",
      "Edit(./docs/status/gate-runs/**)",

      "Write(./.git/**)",
      "Edit(./.git/**)"
    ]
  },

  "hooks": {
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Bash|Write|Edit|NotebookEdit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/pre-tool-use.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Write|Edit|NotebookEdit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/post-tool-use.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SubagentStop": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/subagent-stop.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "Stop": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/.claude/hooks/stop-gate.sh"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
